   299→/* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
   300→/*                 Auto-Tuning Service – End-to-End Orchestrator              */
   301→/* -------------------------------------------------------------------------- */
   302→
   303→/// Interval between automatic tuning rounds (default = 30 minutes).
