    30→/// A flattened representation of a hyper-parameter configuration.
    31→///
    32→/// Keys are logical path segments—e.g. `"optimizer.lr"` or `"model.depth"`.
    33→/// Values are JSON blobs to preserve type information (numeric, categorical,
    34→/// string, …).  Using `serde_json::Value` keeps the design flexible without
    35→/// forcing consumers into yet another strongly typed DSL.
    36→pub type HyperParams = HashMap<String, serde_json::Value>;
