     3→//! -----------------------------------------------------------------
     4→//! This module brings together several architectural patterns
     5→//! (Observer, Strategy, Factory) to deliver production-grade,
     6→//! concurrent model monitoring and automated retraining.
     7→//!
     8→//! High-level responsibilities
     9→//! • Collect structured model-performance events
    10→//! • Notify interested observers in a thread-safe fashion
    11→//! • Decide—based on configurable policies—whether a model
    12→//!   should be retrained
    13→//! • Execute hyper-parameter tuning experiments using a pluggable
    14→//!   strategy pattern
    15→//! • Persist experiment metadata for lineage & auditability
    16→//!
    17→//! In real deployments this module plugs into other layers such as
    18→//! the Model Registry, Feature-Ops, and Serving-Ops, but remains
    19→//! fully self-contained here for demonstration purposes.
